<p>Realistic expectations keep you from chasing the wrong metric.</p>
<p>After completing all 7 steps, you should expect:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>AI Search channel visible in reports within 1 hour.</strong> GA4 usually rebuilds channel groups within 30 minutes, though it can take up to 24 hours on large properties.</li>
<li><strong>Historical data backfilled within 24 hours.</strong> Your AI Search channel will show sessions from up to 50 months ago, which is when GA4 launched for most properties.</li>
